# Retired Legacy HOL Infinitary Name

The older countably infinitary query layer was a predicate-code fragment, not a
real Church-style HOL infinitary semantics.

Use `Mettapedia.Logic.PLNWorldModelPredCodeInfinitary` instead.

This module intentionally re-exports nothing, so the public `HOL` namespace no
longer aliases predicate-code semantics.
